Package: eprdados
Type: Package
Title: Datasets for teaching Landscape Ecology
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Darren",
           family = "Norris",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "dnorris75@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "")) 
           )
Maintainer: Darren Norris <dnorris75@gmail.com>
Description: Diverse spatial datasets for demonstrating and teaching  data analysis used in Landscape Ecology. 
    It includes R data of class sf (defined by the package 'sf') and rast ('terra').
    It also contains data stored in a range of file formats including GeoTiff and GeoPackage. 
    Some of the datasets are designed to illustrate specific analysis techniques.
